### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8201/iam

### Actuator Health
GET http://localhost:8201/actuator/health

### Prometheus Metrics
GET http://localhost:8201/actuator/prometheus

### Stress OOM (1MB chunks, 100ms delay)
GET http://localhost:8201/stress/oom?sizeInMB=1&delayMs=100

### Clear Memory
GET http://localhost:8201/stress/clear
